Package: taxonAlign
Title: Combine multiple taxonomic references to create a personalised taxonomic resource for fuzzy matching of taxonomic names
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Elizabeth", "Wenk", role = c("aut", "ctb", "cph"), email = "e.wenk@unsw.edu.au", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5640-5910")),
    person(given = "Fonti", family = "Kar", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "f.kar@unsw.edu.au", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2760-3974"))
    )
Description: This package provides functions that enables users to: 
  1) create their own taxonomic resource by flexibly combining distinct taxonomic references together
  and 2) to match taxonomic lists to the user's specified taxonomic resource to maxinise alignment coverage. 
